# SkyBridge Travels Reservation Management System

SkyBridge Travels Reservation Management System is a first-year university software engineering project developed to simulate the day-to-day operations of a real-world airline ticket agency. The system is designed as an internal management information system (MIS) that handles airline reservations, passenger management, flight searching, booking operations, payment processing, ticket generation, and operational workflows using a realistic agency-based business model.

---

## Technology Stack

### Frontend
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript

### Backend
- Pure PHP

### Database
- MySQL

